Date: Mon, Sep 10, 2012 at 2:41 PM<br>Subject: [liberationtech] Two Calls for Proposals within Information and Communication Technology<br>To: &quot;<a href="mailto:liberationtech@...">liberationtech@...</a>&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:liberationtech@...">liberationtech@...</a>&gt;, &quot;<a href="mailto:open-development@...">open-development@...</a>&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:open-development@...">open-development@...</a>&gt;<br>

